The next time you casually open your mouth to describe something, a small, red, wooden box, your brain is actively, mathematically sorting the physical persistence of the universe in real time.

724
00:47:44,040 --> 00:47:53,440
You are feeling the gravitational pull of reality, separating the fleeting illusions of your own opinion from the hard, undeniable substance of the object itself.

